                <head>[Memorandum.]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-sibling-dates" calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1866-05-26">undated</date>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Secretary will for the present reserve himself in regard to the communication
                    of General Santa Anna. He recognizes, however, the personal kindness of the
                    general. After a time Mr. Seward may recur to the subject.</p>
            </div>
